data.description:
Where are all the horse lovers at? This one is set up and ready for you and your animals, kick off you shoes and enjoy the
Colorado sunset. One will truly appreciate the circle drive, horse pens and runs, tack room, horse walker, arena and a shop to fit all
your extra toy's. Extra building is being used as their rec room but the opportunities are endless. The arena is set up and ready to
use how ever fit. Walk in the house and you will find a open floor plan, plenty of storage and space for everyone. Truly not
enough room or time to list what all this property offer so schedule your showing today, Sellers are Motivated!
